{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/reactStudy_3/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"redux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux\" aria-label=\"redux permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>자바스크립트로 구동되는 어플리케이션에서 예측 가능한 상태관리를 도와주는 상태관리 라이브러리</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state\" aria-label=\"state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>State</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>state는 크게 3가지로 구분할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>구분</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n<th>방법</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Local State</td>\n<td>하나의 컴포넌트에 영향을 미치는 상태</td>\n<td>useState(), useReducer()</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Cross-Component State</td>\n<td>여러개의 컴포넌트에 영향을 미치는 상태</td>\n<td>prop chains</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Would Wide State</td>\n<td>전체, 대부분의 컴포넌트에 영향을 미치는 상태 ex) authentication status</td>\n<td>prop chains</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>2, 3에 해당하는 경우 <strong>React Context, Redux</strong>를 사용해 해결한다.</p>\n<p>Context를 사용해 2,3번을 해결할 수 있지만 크게 2가지 단점이 존재</p>\n<p><strong>1. Complex Setup / Management</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>여러개의 ContextProvider컴포넌트가 생기면서 관리의 어려움</li>\n<li>여러개의 Provider Component를 생성해 복잡한 JSX구문</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2. Performance</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"장점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%A5%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"장점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>장점</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>상태를 예측 가능하게 만듬</li>\n<li>테스트나 디버깅에 용이</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"특징\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\" aria-label=\"특징 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Single source of truth</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>애플리케이션의 모든 상태는 하나의 저장소 안에 하나의 객체 트리 구조로 저장</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>State is read-only</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>상태는 읽기전용(불변) 데이터이며, 오직 액션만 상태를 변경할 수 있다</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>변화를 일으키는 함수, 리듀서는 순수 함수여야 한다</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이전 상태와 액션을 받아 다음 상태를 반환하는 순수 함수</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>순수함수: 반환(reture)값이 전달 인자(argument) 값에만 의존하는 함수</p>\n<h2 id=\"핵심-개념\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90\" aria-label=\"핵심 개념 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>핵심 개념</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-state\" aria-label=\"1 state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. State</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Redux API에서는 보통 저장소에 의해 관리되고 getState()에 의해 반환되는 하나의 상태값</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"2-store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-store\" aria-label=\"2 store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Store</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>애플리케이션의 상태 값들을 내장하고 있다 (상태가 관리되는 하나의 공간)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"3-action\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-action\" aria-label=\"3 action permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Action</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>태를 변화시키려는 의도를 표현하는 객체</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>어떤 형태의 액션이 행해질지 표시하는 <strong>type 필드</strong>를 가져야 한다</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-reducer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-reducer\" aria-label=\"4 reducer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Reducer</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>상태를 변화시키는 로직이 담긴 함수. 현재 상태와 Action을 이용해 다음 상태를 만들어 낸다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"5-dispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-dispatch\" aria-label=\"5 dispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Dispatch</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>액션이나 비동기 액션을 받는 함수</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.redux.js.org/understanding/thinking-in-redux/glossary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">추가로 알아야 할 용어</a></p>\n<p><strong>Tip!!</strong><br>\n비동기를 지원하는 <a href=\"https://github.com/redux-saga/redux-saga\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Redux-Sage</a> (추가로 정리 할 예정)</p>\n<h1 id=\"routing-deployment-nextjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#routing-deployment-nextjs\" aria-label=\"routing deployment nextjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Routing, Deployment, NextJS</h1>\n<h1 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/best-react/learn/lecture/28517643#overview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Udemy - React 완벽 가이드 with Redux, Next.js, TypeScript</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ko.redux.js.org/understanding/thinking-in-redux/three-principles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">3가지 원칙 - redux doc</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ko.redux.js.org/understanding/thinking-in-redux/glossary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">용어집 - redux doc</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Redux 자바스크립트로 구동되는 어플리케이션에서 예측 가능한 상태관리를 도와주는 상태관리 라이브러리 State state는 크게 3가지로 구분할 수 있다. 구분 설명 방법 Local State 하나의 컴포넌트에 영향을 미치는 상태 useState(…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#redux\">Redux</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#state\">State</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#%EC%9E%A5%EC%A0%90\">장점</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\">특징</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90\">핵심 개념</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#1-state\">1. State</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#2-store\">2. Store</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#3-action\">3. Action</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#4-reducer\">4. Reducer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#5-dispatch\">5. Dispatch</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#routing-deployment-nextjs\">Routing, Deployment, NextJS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/reactStudy_3/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/reactStudy_3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Redux, Routing","date":"Sep 05, 2022","tags":["React"],"keywords":["React"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/reactStudy_3/","series":[{"slug":"/reactStudy_1/","title":"React 핵심 기능","num":1},{"slug":"/reactStudy_2/","title":"React Hooks & Http Request","num":2},{"slug":"/reactStudy_3/","title":"React Re